verbose_text: Levels of ammonium also varied over the whole period, lower values being observed at the end of the season (September 2009 : 1.92 mg kg -1 +/- 0.16; October 2010 : 5.86 mg kg -1 +/- 0.63), and higher ones at the start (April 2009 : 13.3 mg kg -1 +/- 1.13; April 2010 : 15.3 mg kg -1 +/- 1.01).
